<!-- Apply loadable open sans fonts for almost everything in Poweramp. Keep few styles as is just to demonstrate that
     NOTE: many *_Text styles here also sets "sp" size. This is because original Poweramp skin has some text sizes set in dp which are not scalable
     according to user settings. While this gives a bit more consistent look, here we use sp sizes which will mostly match default skin sizes for default
     Android system font size settings, but will also grow/shrink according to that setting
-->
